Title: Enacts the "reimagining long-term care task force" to create a task force to study the state of long-term care services in this state
Summary: Enacts the "reimagining long-term care task force act" to create a task force to study the state of long-term care services in this state.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to enacting the "reimagining long-term care task force" to create a task force to study the state of long-term care services in this state
